basic_content:
Credit Card

Basic

A credit card is a line of credit that can be used to borrow money to make purchases, transfer balances and get cash advances, with the agreement that you'll pay back the money borrowed.

Features

  • Easy Approval
  • Customised card limit
  • Purchasing on EMI
  • Availing Loans during emergency
  • ATM cash withdrawal
  • Discounts and Offers
  • Reward points 8. Secure pay

Eligibility

  • Minimum age - 18 years
  • Minimum salary – 35,000
  • Applicant should either be salaried or self-employed


How to Earn

  1. Suggest Credit Card to everyone who have a regular source of income in your network (friends/ customers)
  2. Click on “Add Lead” Option and choose “Credit Card”.
  3. Provide your customer’s personal details (mobile no, pan no, mail-id, DOB etc.)
  4. Provide your customer’s Professional Details (professions, company name, salary, etc.)
  5. If you are eligible, select a card from the eligible card list
  6. You will earn Upto Rs. 2500 & your commission will reflect in your Banksathi wallet after card successfully collect by your customer.
  7. You will get the commission in your bank account on 15th of every month.

Personal Loan

A personal loan is borrowed to fulfil personal purposes such as medical emergencies, travel, wedding expenditure or debt consolidation.

title: Covid-19 Insurance
sub_title: 1 Lac Rs Coverage for 18 Critical Illnesses
basic_content:
COVID-19 & CI Insurance

Basic

 

COVID-19 & Critical Illnesses Insurance plan covers COVID-19 along with 18 critical illnesses.

 

Coverage

  • Rs 1,00,000 for 18 critical illnesses.
  • Rs 25,000 for COVID-19 & hospitalisation. 

Policy parameters: 

  • Policy Tenure – 1 Years
  • Cover Start date: Premium payment date to Insurer.
  • Age: 10 Year (Min) – 55 Year (Max.)
  • Premium- Rs. 999/year (Including GST)

Child Age:

  • Age should be 1 to 22 years on the date of purchase of the policy.

 

Pre-existing Condition:

  • We can offer this policy to all members with no pre-existing health conditions.

 

Nominee:

  • Age should be greater than 18 & nominee relationships can be: Self, Spouse, Son, Daughter, Mother, Father, Brother, Sister

 

Product Contours: 

  • We will pay the Sum Insured to the Insured Person on the first diagnosis of Covered medical event.
  • For the purpose of this Policy, only Diagnosis made by laboratories authorized by Union Health Ministry of India for COVID-19 testing shall be considered valid.
  • Waiting Period 30 days
  • Pre-existing cover after 4 years
  • 24 Hrs Hospitalization mandatory for COVID

Information Required

  • Name
  • DOB
  • Nominee name
  • DOB of nominee
  • Insured’s relation with nominee
  • Pre-Existing Health Condition

How to Earn

  1. Suggest COVID 19 & CI Insurance to everyone in your network (friends/ customers)
  2. Click on “Add Lead” Option.
  3. Enter customer’s mobile number
  4. Enter customer’s name, DOB, Email-id & Address
  5. If customer want to add more member choose “Yes, I Want” & enter member details
  6. Enter nominee detail & click on “Get Payment link”
  7. Share payment link to the customer
  8. Your commission will be reflected in your Banksathi Wallet after the premium is successfully paid by the customer.

•	Our pixel is getting fired on OTP verification. Afterward, if the user discontinues the journey, then he/she will get a call from the call center team to submit documents, his/her account will open.

•	In case the user proceeds with documentation and submits all documents then the account will be open online. Here, no calling done for cross verification.

•	No frauds, Incase of such activity: fake account opening, misleading communication, Incentivized leads or account opening.

•	Aadhar Card
•	Account number with IFSC Code
•	Signature on paper

sub_title: NULL
basic_content:
Personal Loan

Basic

A personal loan is borrowed to fulfil personal purposes such as medical emergencies, travel, wedding expenditure or debt consolidation.

Features

  • No collateral is required
  • Less documentation
  • Quick disbursement
  • Easy EMI facility
  • Flexible loan tenure

Eligibility

  • Age - 21 to 60 years
  • Monthly salary - Rs. 30,000
  • Minimum Work Experience - 1 year
  • Minimum Work Exp. with current organisation - 6 months

How to Earn

  1. Suggest Personal loan to salaried person in your network (friends/ customers)
  2. Click on “Add Lead” Option and choose “Offer A Personal Loan”.
  3. Provide your customer’s personal details (mobile no, email-id, DOB, Address etc.)
  4. Provide your customer’s existing loan details (if any)
  5. Provide Income details (monthly salary, company name, job vintage, office email, office address)
  6. You will earn Upto 2.25% of loan amount & your commission will reflect in your Banksathi wallet after sanctioned your customer’s loan sanction.
  7. You will get the commission in your bank account on 15th of every month.
